Package: EcoliGenomics
Type: Package
Title: Typing and virulence screening of E coli genomes 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jérôme Ambroise
Maintainer: <jerome.ambroise@uclouvain.be>
Description: This package can be used in order to type (using E coli MLST scheme) and screen (e.g. for the presence of virulence) E coli genomes. The genomes can be either complete or draft (i.e., multiple contigs). To this end, both main functions are 'typemlst' and 'screen_Blast'.
Imports:
	Biostrings,
	GenomicRanges,
	IRanges
